	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You should add a ground fill to the top layer.  In EAGLE, that means creating a polygon that follows the board outline on the top layer, then use the name tool to name it GND, then hit the ratsnest button.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
