		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Do i share much the same way i share miso mosi lines on AVE?? I didn't have to do anything special, although those pins shared gpio. Will it be the exact same for PIC? What kind of design precautions must i take to share a pic icsp with gpio rather than dedicated icsp pins.

		

